rows.label: tev016601_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Leland about his body.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Leland if he's heard any interesting rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0001
rows.name:
You mean this young, virile mimeosome of mine?
I had to go through a lot of trouble to get it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0002
rows.name:
There's some ridiculous rule that everyone has to have
a mimeosome that looks just like their real body.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0003
rows.name:
And if you tell the technicians you want a younger one,
they just insist that it will confuse people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0004
rows.name:
I had to take my request all the way up the chain
of command, and after a great deal of discussion,
they finally gave me permission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0005
rows.name:
I suppose I caused a lot of trouble for a lot of people,
but I won't give them cause to regret giving me back
my youth. I'm gonna mine all sorts of new ore for 'em![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0006
rows.name:
Cole Family Rule Number Three: As long as a man is
getting results at work, everything's fine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0009
rows.name:
A band of Wrothians is living in a cave somewhere
in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0010
rows.name:
I heard that from some Nopon who live in the region.
What do you think they're doing in a place like that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0011
rows.name:
I can't explain it, but I know they're strong fighters,
so you'd best be on guard around them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Leland if he has any interesting news.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0012
rows.name:
I saw a strange Wrothian while I was on a mission in
Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0013
rows.name:
You know those ruins on the sandbank out there?
Well, I was over in that area when I saw the fellow
leaping at indigens and fighting them barehanded![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0014
rows.name:
He'd beat one silly for a few seconds, then move on to
the next. And he kept at it for the entire time I was
watching him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0015
rows.name:
I don't know if he was hunting them or what,
but whatever he was doing, he's one tough bastard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Leland if he has any interesting news.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0016
rows.name:
You know the Wrothian I used to see out in Oblivia?
I haven't seen him around lately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0017
rows.name:
From what I hear, he's traveling around Mira and
undertaking some kind of training journey.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0018
rows.name:
I hope I get a chance to meet him again.
I really admire his spirit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Leland if he has any interesting news.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0019
rows.name:
So the Wrothian I always used to see out in Oblivia?
Turns out his name is Gi Zang.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0020
rows.name:
I just happened to run into him the other day on the
Ma-non ship. Boy, did we ever have lots to talk about![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0021
rows.name:
Apparently he really WAS traveling throughout Mira
and training in different places.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016601_MSG0022
rows.name:
What spirit! If I didn't have my missions, I'd head off
on a geological survey and travel throughout Mira like
he did. No one holding me back! No, sir![ST:wait ]
